ATK_STATE_ACTIVE is a means to indicate that an object which is not focusable and not selectable is the currently-active item within its parent container.

ATK_STATE_ARMED has been deprecated since ATK-2.16 and should not be used in newly-written code.

Extensions/StateType.html#/s:So12AtkStat.name: busy

This state may be used by implementors of Document to indicate that content loading is underway. It also may indicate other ‘pending’ conditions; clients may wish to interrogate this object when the ATK_STATE_BUSY flag is removed.

Extensions/StateType.html#/s:So12AtkStat.name: checked
